    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a reliable choice for someone needing a steady daily driver. While it runs well, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some fading in the paint. The interior is clean but has visible wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It is a solid, functional car that has been well-maintained mechanically despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
