    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it truly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s in pristine, mint condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found anywhere! I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. It's ready for its next adventure\u2014come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
